The paper proposes a novel approach for constraint-based graphical user interface (GUI) layout, which is a topic related to human-computer interaction (HCI) and graphics (GR). The paper also discusses the design patterns and editor for the proposed approach, which falls under software development (SD) and programming languages (PL). Additionally, the paper mentions the efficient runtime solving of the ORC specifications, which is related to computational linguistics (CL). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.HCI and cs.GR, followed by cs.SD, cs.PL, and cs.CL.
